    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你有多善于观察？你能通过揭示线索生存10天吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/675d6dc83b5734c05ac4f2ead6dc5b4f.poster.avif?t=1770676677\" width=640 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/675d6dc83b5734c05ac4f2ead6dc5b4f.webm?t=1770676677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/675d6dc83b5734c05ac4f2ead6dc5b4f.mp4?t=1770676677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为黑手党的前成员，你试图对抗老大作证，而他则竭尽全力要除掉你。为了生存，你必须在存放车辆的地下车库中寻找破坏的证据，以确认是否有人曾经来过。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果一切正常，你可以上车，但如果看到任何可疑的东西，立即返回电梯并呼叫帮助！如果你放松警惕，你的生命将岌岌可危！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/1c5e5a9ca79dd1899aa59db6787701de.poster.avif?t=1770676677\" width=632 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/1c5e5a9ca79dd1899aa59db6787701de.webm?t=1770676677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/1c5e5a9ca79dd1899aa59db6787701de.mp4?t=1770676677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在这款密室逃脱风格的游戏中，你可以测试你的观察技能。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Targeted -10 Days结合了写实主义和黑色电影的体验，设定在类似黑手党的环境中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏提供多种难度级别：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >普通：一个平衡模式，可在10-30分钟内完成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >困难模式：更多关卡和更多异常。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >T-99不可能模式：专为硬核观察者设计的99天挑战，拥有意想不到的曲折。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超自然异常模式</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/c8e57a07a1d18970315775adbbe50206.avif?t=1770676677\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras_big/c8e57a07a1d18970315775adbbe50206.avif?t=1770676677 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可重玩性：</strong> 超过230个线索等待被发现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你有多快？</strong> 我们内建的速通计时器可以让你与其他玩家和朋友竞争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>存档。</strong> 你可以从上次中断的地方继续。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与朋友一起玩：</strong> 虽然不包括多人模式，但你可以使用Steam远程同乐与朋友分享控制权。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成就：</strong> 你喜欢把游戏玩到极致吗？Targeted的成就系统会让你忙上好几个小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>低系统需求：</strong> 该游戏自始至终优化了低配置电脑的性能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>手工动画过场动画。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你准备好挑战了吗？只有最敏锐的眼睛才能生存一天！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/ad09d6c8e83dabe8e4d9ca452900d7d0.poster.avif?t=1770676677\" width=640 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/ad09d6c8e83dabe8e4d9ca452900d7d0.webm?t=1770676677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075050/extras/ad09d6c8e83dabe8e4d9ca452900d7d0.mp4?t=1770676677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>保持警惕！在这款游戏中你是目标！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>购买时请注意，游戏在单一地点进行，根据你的观察技能可能会很快完成。然而，由于我们的无数异常情况，它可以多次重玩，并在几个小时后给你展示一些新的东西。</i></p>",
